TMCAS: TMCAS is a simulator for an MQTT Based 
anti-collision prototype for railway networks.
Authors: B. Mishra, A. Pati, B. Mishra
*************************************************//
********************
System Requirements
*******************
Hardware
	1. RAM 2GB(Min)
	2. HDD 100 MB (Min)
	3. Resolution ( 1920 x 1080 )
Software
	1. Windows 8.1 or Higher
	2. .Net Framework 4.5.2 or higher
	3. Active Internet Connection
